snippet.title: U.S Game & Watch Portable commercial
snippet.description: Early 80s. Commercial for the Timeout game from Game & Watch (Ball/Silver) portable. Includes a fanatic Game & Watch's ederly man. I like much of the Game & Watch portables.   Comercial americano do jogo Timeout (Tempo Esgotado) para o portatil Game & Watch. Eu gosto muito dos portateis Game & Watch.
